ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely I would recommend it - a challenging course covering a very difficult writer and the thorough unpacking of the difficult political, literary and social themes of his work.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course provided not only extremely thought provoking content and discussion but also emphasized how to read very charged and difficult texts critically and in their political context. These skills are invaluable for constructing arguments and evaluating them for my own research.
